## 8. Commandos Úteis para o Agente

```bash
# Verificar estado
git status
git log --oneline -5

# Verificar MCPs
python3 scripts/verify-mcp.py --all

# Criar novo MCP
python3 -c "from constructor import create_mcp; create_mcp('id', name='Nome')"

# Atualizar lockfile
python3 -c "from catalog import list_mcp_ids, read_manifest, manifest_hash, read_lockfile, write_lockfile; lock = read_lockfile(); [...]"

# Validar manifesto
python3 -c "from validator import validate_manifest_file; print(validate_manifest_file('mcps/<id>/mcp.json'))"

# Rodar testes
python3 -m pytest mcps/<id>/tests/ registry/tests/

# Disparar workflow individual
gh workflow run mcp-runtime.yml -f mcp_id=<id> --repo camillanapoles/mcps-as-objects
```
